{
  "stem": "18474.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Dump it, we use to keep the manure from the horses and the cows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was-- this was the way it done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They used to send us in a little bit of water, a few potatoes, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and it got so bad from the disease we had that my pants from the pus was stiff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They soaked in with pus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have no hair on my legs, not one hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's all new skin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it got real bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we didn't want them to know inside that we are diseased because if they'll find out that we have a disease, you might want to chase us out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they never knew it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One night, my sister-- we had a-- a Polish family there-- fine people, because they was--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right not in between, but a kilometer away, maybe a kilometer and a quarter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was living on the main highway there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Federovich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was not a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was like a-- we used to call him a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] used to do little things, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, my father went over there to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, look, and even when we seen him, we didn't know what to-- you know, like we--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--took him out from a grave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hiding, and he went over there to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was diseased a little bit too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was it?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told him, he says, I'm going to make you up a-- a sap-- a-- from sulphur and fit-- pig, pig fat, mix it all up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You come tomorrow, he says, I'll have it ready for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't trust too many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my sister went over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
